high_descs: Turn right and face the table on the left.
Pick up the spoon from the table.
Turn left and go to the stove.
Put the spoon in the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot and spoon from the stove.
Turn right and go back to the table.
Set the pot and spoon back on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the spoon in the pot and back on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go forward to the table on the left that has the toaster on it.
Pick up the spoon that is on the table between the two salt shakers.
Turn to the left and go to the stove.
Put the spoon in the pot on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the pot with the spoon in it.
Turn to the right and go to the white table on the left that has the toaster on it.
Put the pot on the table to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spoon in it on a table.

high_descs: Move to stand in front of the white table against the wall.
Pick up the spoon that's to the left of the blue plate.
Carry the spoon to stand in front of the stove.
Place the spoon in the pan that's on the front right burner.
Pick up the pan with the spoon in it from the stove.
Carry the pan and spoon back to the white table by the wall.
Place the pan with the spoon in it on the back left corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan with a spoon inside to the white table.
